column2: SELECT to upload -- the results to the SAS (Science Archive Server) for FITS file retrieval. SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.probPSF FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.ra BETWEEN # - # AND # + # AND p.dec BETWEEN # - # AND # + #
